--USEFUL DIRECTORIES--
WEB PAGE DOCROOT --> /var/www/html/
VIRTULA HOST WEB PAGE DOCROOT --> /var/www/vhost/DOMAIN/docroot/
HTTPD CONFIGURATION --> /etc/httpd

--USAGE--
EDIT HTTPD CONFIGURATION --> select the HTTPD option
EDIT EXISTING VHOST CONFIGURATION --> select the ADD option again, the configuration file will be updated
UPDATE EXISTING USER PASSWORD --> select the ADD USER option again, then input the new password
